body:
2nd attempt for Flink streaming connector for redis. This pull request is for only sink part of the connector. @rmetzger , @mjsax can u plz review. the previous attempt was https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1580. With the updated code 
1. we can use most of the redis data types, 
2. we can use it for redis single server, cluster or sentinels. 
3. the pooling options can be set.

``` java
public static class RedisDataMapper implements RedisMapper<Tuple2<String, String>>{
    @Override
    public RedisCommandDescription getDataTypeDescription() {
        return new RedisCommandDescription(RedisCommand.RPUSH);
    }
    @Override
    public String getKeyFromData(Tuple2<String, String> data) {
        return data.f0;
    }
    @Override
    public String getValueFromData(Tuple2<String, String> data) {
        return data.f1;
    }
}
RedisSink<Tuple2<String, String>> redisSink = new RedisSink<>(jedisPoolConfig,
            new RedisDataMapper());
```

right now we can use data types:

``` java
public enum RedisDataType {
    STRING, HASH, LIST, SET, SORTED_SET, HYPER_LOG_LOG, PUBSUB
}
```

``` java
public enum RedisCommand {
  LPUSH(RedisDataType.LIST),
  RPUSH(RedisDataType.LIST),
  SADD(RedisDataType.SET),
  SET(RedisDataType.STRING),
  PFADD(RedisDataType.HYPER_LOG_LOG),
  PUBLISH(RedisDataType.PUBSUB),
  ZADD(RedisDataType.SORTED_SET),
  HSET(RedisDataType.HASH);
}
```

for single redis server:

``` java
JedisPoolConfig poolConfig = new JedisPoolConfig.Builder().setHost("127.0.0.1").build();
```

for cluster:

``` java
JedisClusterConfig clusterConfig = new JedisClusterConfig.Builder().setNodes(...).build();
```

for sentinels:

``` java
JedisSentinelConfig.Builder builder = new JedisSentinelConfig.Builder();
Set<String> sentinels = new HashSet<>();
sentinels.add("127.0.0.1");
builder.setSentinels(sentinels).setMasterName("master").build();
```

we can also set pooling options:

``` java
builder.setMaxTotal(1).setMinIdle(1).setMaxTotal(1).build();
```

plz tell me what else we can improve.

thanks
subhankar

